{"tid":1995860,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨衛軍於山東街拘捕2人 車上搜出反光衣頭盔","createTime":"2020-04-30T14:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T15:38:52.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2e5d4fcb2712d8a0737368fed0a7ca9a3c28f6","tid":1995860,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"警方於山東街拘捕2人 車上搜出反光衣頭盔<br />\n30.04.2020 22:12<br />\n<br />\n今日是港鐵太子站831事件8個月，晚上有大批防暴警員在太子站多個出口戒備，在B1出口築起封鎖線，警員大多配備盾牌。警員晚上多次在彌敦道截查途人，包括手持鮮花的年輕人，及持美國國旗的市民。有區議員在封鎖線外圍設置紙箱，讓市民放下鮮花。警方在旺角警署以揚聲器廣播，指現場市民違反「限聚令」，要求立即解散。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在山東街及洗衣街交界，一架警車晚上9時許截停一架私家車，拘捕車上2人。現場消息指，警方認為私家車形跡可疑，在車上發現一批反光衣和頭盔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284441&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1284441%26csid%3D261_341&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=a6835c7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284441&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"194411862437953a7ecf49d1688b151817922c56","tid":1995860,"uid":24345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"又搞鳩first aid 手足"},{"pid":"dc7373c5223cf1429c75ef024314ce20ca8faa00","tid":1995860,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"194411862437953a7ecf49d1688b151817922c56","tid":1995860,"uid":24345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"又搞鳩first aid 手足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"（超長文）手足請入，五一黃金週所掩蓋的重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1995782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1995782</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n泛民/本土： 一齊初選 = 分開初選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1990193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1990193</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n初選其實係免費嘅！？！？<br />\n<a href=\"http